{"tid":1626603,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"下一個戰場 - 選戰","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:13:40.000Z","uid":237890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"779ff03f285397243a4d100a902a26332213a4e9","tid":1626603,"uid":237890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:02:58.000Z","msg":"留意番 , 唔好淨係掛住蒙面同裝修 , 選戰已經開始左 !<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好再俾D <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">□□</span> 當選 !</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2019%2Fchi%2Findex.html&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=38fa88e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/index.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">再送你一條熊仔頭打氣片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RjvsMU6batM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRjvsMU6batM&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=04ac86c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RjvsMU6batM</a></span>"},{"pid":"9d97e3c7fca94f3c69aa7cb5ff2f06556f7e4c79","tid":1626603,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"聽曰港島記住係和平遊行<br />\n盡量吸多D和理非出黎<br />\n和理非唔好怕無不反對通知書<br />\n香港已經唔講法律<br />\n有不反對通知書都照拉鳩你架啦<br />\n所以聽日為香港全世界出黎港島<br />\n勇和一家目標300萬人和平遊行<br />\n畀人知道香港人係和平嘅<br />\n暴力嘅係政府<br />\n要吸多D國際支持<br />\n<br />\n同時我唔反對衝衝子去衝<br />\n但記住要散水返左屋企先<br />\n避免畀狗圍無路走唔到<br />\n返左屋企之後再係屋企步行範圍內快閃游擊<br />\n拆鐵拆政府建築幫中資國企裝修<br />\n裝修到星期二開唔到門就變相三罷<br />\n唔好等有狗出現就要散水轉場<br />\n記住我地優勢係人多機動性高<br />\n攰同餓就返屋企食飯休息回滿升先再第日出過<br />\n有唔對路就返屋企訓覺唔好送頭<br />\n<br />\n幫手推POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1626523/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1626523/page/1</a>"}]}